{"id": 539, "genre": 1001, "title": "12天只带手机不带钱？你还想给实验者添什么麻烦？", "description": "十一期间，我们的实验者将不带钱去往5个TA从未去过的闽南城市，TA要怎么买吃的？TA要怎么坐公交？快再进来出点馊主意吧。", "record_count": 4103, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606145055KRcYeMGSoETWml8s.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-09-22T09:26:28Z", "options": [{"id": 12544, "content": "诺基亚", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 186315}, {"id": 12800, "content": "约个炮", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117214}, {"id": 12545, "content": "老年机", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194200}, {"id": 12546, "content": "给身边的10个小伙伴手写邮寄一封信~", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194259}, {"id": 13826, "content": "不准开机！！！哈哈?哈?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212018}, {"id": 12547, "content": "只可以使用百度钱包", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114588}, {"id": 12549, "content": "反正便利店可以微信支付，公交可以用手机刷，打车可以支付宝。不会死。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 12551, "content": "沿街卖艺赚钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194279}, {"id": 12552, "content": "每天的步行距离限制在3000米之内", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194285}, {"id": 12553, "content": "只准用2G", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194299}, {"id": 12554, "content": "打工换钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194318}, {"id": 12555, "content": "不准自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1201889}, {"id": 14603, "content": "有种就去云贵地区试试。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222031}, {"id": 12812, "content": "欢迎到闽南来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66381}, {"id": 13068, "content": "所有账户包括支付宝和微信账户都为0", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201382}, {"id": 12557, "content": "手机不准上网", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194340}, {"id": 12558, "content": "手机不要插卡，不要连wifi", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 48543}, {"id": 23566, "content": "头像换成女的加人要红包", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292772}, {"id": 12559, "content": "我喜欢获得表扬", "image": "img/option/option/20160604235033r3Mb7iaUeDvnX0oP.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194267}, {"id": 12560, "content": "找一份咖啡馆的小时工，赚取下一站旅行的费用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 190109}, {"id": 12562, "content": "手机事先要欠费", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181688}, {"id": 12563, "content": "不能穿衣服！", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156145}, {"id": 13076, "content": "能不能下一款统计手机使用时间的应用，我记得有款应用可以统计使用时间，碎片化程度。毕竟这是一场旅行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55871}, {"id": 12565, "content": "带盒粉笔，路边写上「求好心人赞助好奇心日报饭钱和路费，所有款项找好奇心日报报销」", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58260}, {"id": 12567, "content": "把手机卖了买吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194395}, {"id": 12823, "content": "坐公交，搭地铁，路边吃个快餐，买点当地的纪念品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166879}, {"id": 12569, "content": "在那里哭泣", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194513}, {"id": 13338, "content": "手机电量在第十二天还得保持60%", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205288}, {"id": 13595, "content": "别拿银行卡什么都不要带不许手机联网", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209267}, {"id": 12572, "content": "只